        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Bancroft Gherardi (1832-1903 was born in Louisiana. He entered the United States Naval Academy in 1852, was appointed Commandant of the Brooklyn Navy Yard in 1884.</p>
        </bioghist>
